He began his journalism career as an intern with The Times&#8217;s bureau in Kabul, Afghanistan, in 2010, before moving on to work for Al Jazeera English in Doha and then pursue magazine writing. He returned to The Times as a senior correspondent in October 2016. Born in Kabul, he received a degree in history from Columbia University." />
